    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/7538b911f7c8633c4f828cfb086a8ca3.poster.avif?t=1765354273\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/7538b911f7c8633c4f828cfb086a8ca3.webm?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/7538b911f7c8633c4f828cfb086a8ca3.mp4?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Den of Wolves》是一款合作抢盗类第一人称射击游戏，你和好友将以职业犯罪高手的身份混迹于法外创新区中途城。在这个企业天堂里，敌对商业实体的“脏活”需求日益渐长，而你会借势而上。<br><br>我们通过《Den of Wolves》打造内容丰富的科技惊险流派游戏——以回合制合作抢盗射击游戏为雏形，无论你选择挑战 20 分钟，还是 2 小时，凡过之处必要回响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/2a0e5218caba1b1b5a22419f37c573f9.poster.avif?t=1765354273\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/2a0e5218caba1b1b5a22419f37c573f9.webm?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/2a0e5218caba1b1b5a22419f37c573f9.mp4?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>策划和执行工业谍报、蓄意破坏、盗窃和暗杀行动。召集成员，选定最佳方案，获得武器、设备和情报，渗透进安全系统并实施抢劫。<br><br>你的团队将在光怪陆离的场景中体验潜行、全面行动和卷土重来的全过程。<br><br>与手下团队联手在《Den of Wolves》的乱世中获得赃物——同时还有机会在行动期间结识更多同道中人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/8fa0f210a7743d61e49b1eb7e213ad8a.poster.avif?t=1765354273\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/8fa0f210a7743d61e49b1eb7e213ad8a.webm?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/8fa0f210a7743d61e49b1eb7e213ad8a.mp4?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>中途岛是由全球企业精英财团建设的法外创新区，专门用来应对深度学习人工智能对全球化数据安全造成的威胁。<br><br>由于没有人权机构出面平乱，他们研发出基于人脑的新式数据传输和存储概念——这种技术与传统网络架构完全不同，人工智能根本无法操纵它。<br><br>随着安全保障为市场带来了信心，中途市已发展成为不断扩张的国际贸易神经中枢——这是充满机遇的新土地；而机遇是乘间作祸的温床……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/551d17280993111bfd25f3327ec0c99e.poster.avif?t=1765354273\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/551d17280993111bfd25f3327ec0c99e.webm?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/551d17280993111bfd25f3327ec0c99e.mp4?t=1765354273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>作为开发工作室，10 Chambers 致力于打造合作射击类游戏；这是刻在我们 DNA 里的使命。我们竭尽所能构思合作玩法和引人入胜的故事内容——精益求精，不求一时之快。我们会尽力在研发过程中为大家送上最新动态。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818140/extras/4862768907a18e1ad76ccb9dfa4d8b80.avif?t=1765354273\" width=616 height=200 /></span>",
